## Executive Overview

STARFRAME SF-1 represents the first complete implementation of structural intelligence within the PI220 ecosystem.

Unlike traditional aerospace structures which exist primarily to support payloads and propulsion systems, STARFRAME SF-1 transforms the airframe into an active operational component capable of participating in:

* Load management
* Aerodynamic optimization
* Thermal distribution
* Energy recovery
* Telecommunications routing
* Autonomous structural adaptation

The STARFRAME philosophy introduces a new engineering principle:

> Structure is no longer passive.

> Structure becomes intelligence.

STARFRAME SF-1 establishes the foundational architecture later expanded within:

* Boeing 220-X
* Boeing 220-Y
* Boeing 220-G Lattice Core
* Boeing 220-G Global

