## 1. Development Objectives

The primary objectives were:

### Structural Adaptability

Create an airframe capable of dynamically distributing loads.

### Lifecycle Extension

Reduce fatigue accumulation.

### Energy Integration

Enable structural participation in energy systems.

### Serviceability

Allow modular replacement of damaged sections.

### Mission Scalability

Support future aerospace and orbital architectures.

